thread.title: Andrew Wilmot
thread.title_full: GO Rentals New Zealand reviewed by Andrew Wilmot

author: Andrew Wilmot
title: Andrew Wilmot
text: Efficient clean shuttle buses between the Go Rental Depots located just offsite from the airports, and the Airport Arrivals / Departures. Car was ready and collected on our arrival at Auckland airport, and dropped off 17 days later at Queenstown Airport, South Island. Excellent experience with GO Rentals from start to finish of the hire. Good clean economical Toyota Yaris. Great friendly helpful staff. I highly recommend Go Rentals for their excellent service, which helped make a fantastic holiday in beautiful New Zealand.
